{
  "name": "rhythm-chamber",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Rhythm Chamber is an AI-powered data analytics application that focuses on what your data says about youâ€”think Spotify Wrapped but year-round and actually personalized. Bring your own intelligence: run local models or your own keys, with demo mode and template-driven profile synthesis for instant exploration. Upload your JSON/ZIP export or connect Spotify for quick snapshots. The app is 100% client-side; only your chosen AI provider and music service see your data.",
